headline: Campbell’s to Sell noosa Business to Lakeview Farms
summary: CAMDEN, N.J., November 12, 2024--Campbell Soup Company (NASDAQ:CPB) (Campbell’s) today announced an agreement to sell the noosa yoghurt business to Lakeview Farms, LLC, a manufacturer of fresh dips, desserts and specialty products. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
